metadata.name: Isolation
metadata.description:
Hidden away so deep and so isolated in the forests and lakes of Plitvice National Park, Croatia, it takes serious effort to find this place. It's the kind of place you go when you don't want to be found. 

Solitude guaranteed.

his photo was taken on September 22nd, 2021.

Isolation; artwork by Nick van Eijk
